data.description: Dreaming of a multi-family property that offers both convenience and income-potential? Look no further! Introducing 106 Sherman Ave, a hidden gem nestled in the heart of the highly desirable Jersey City Heights community. This unique property features not one, but TWO incredible structures. The main building boasts three meticulously maintained units, each offering a comfortable living space. Whether you're looking for a charming place to call your own or an investment opportunity that practically pays for itself, this is it! But wait, there's more! Step into the modern 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom single-family carriage house tucked away in the rear of the property. It's privacy was designed with your comfort in mind. Location, location, location! Jersey City Heights offers an array of shops, restaurants, and picturesque parks right at your doorstep. And the best part? New York City is just a short and easy commute away, making this property perfect for city dwellers. Do not miss out on this incredible opportunity to live in one unit and generate rental income from the others. It's a win-win scenario that you won't want to pass up! Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience it for yourself. Act fast, because opportunities like this do not come around often!
